### MV UNION
Returns all unique values from both input fields. Returns `null` if either field is null.

```esql
ROW a = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5], b = [2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
| EVAL finalValue = MV_UNION(a, b)
| KEEP finalValue
```
